{
  "texts": [
    "For brevity only binary actuation is shown.",
    "Even when a4-a6 are ignored, the sensor reading and its overall boundaries will remains unchanged.",
    "However, ignoring the non-nearest neighbors might result in a loss in detection resolution.",
    "This further depends on whether those actuators are capable of affecting the sensor reading.",
    "Any included actuator whose states does not affect the sensor reading may be considered as a do not care actuator."
  ]
}